data.description: Look at this Beautiful well taken care of HOME!This home is open concept with vaulted ceilings that provides ample living room and kitchen. House has tile throughout the common areas and clean carpet in bedrooms and living room. Kitchen features pantry, granite countertops, and island with bar.House has split floor plan with 4 bedroom 2bath 3 car garage. Interior was painted a yr ago, beautiful back yard with lush green lawn and bushes for entertaining guests. Call for appointment today.
